CustomField.description: Label to use for the 'submit' button in the survey response interface.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Specify the label to be displayed on the 'Submit' button in the survey response interface. This button is typically shown on the final page of the survey and allows participants to submit their completed responses. Choose a clear and engaging label that encourages participants to finalize and submit their survey.
CustomField.label: Submit Button Label
